### DispatchMindAI — Demo Request Scenarios
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000
### Real data: hub_id=129 (high-volume hub, 1022 parcels/90d), area_id=1748

@base_url = http://localhost:3000

# ─── Health ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check
GET {{base_url}}/health

# ─── Dispatch ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Recommend Dispatch — high-volume hub/area (has real data)
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/dispatch/recommend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hub_id": 129,
  "area_id": 1748,
  "parcel_value": 1500,
  "weight": 1.2,
  "sla_days": 3
}

###

### Recommend Dispatch — another active hub/area combo
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/dispatch/recommend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hub_id": 136,
  "area_id": 1245,
  "parcel_value": 2500,
  "weight": 2.0,
  "sla_days": 2
}

###

### Dispatch History — last 50 decisions
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/dispatch/history

# ─── Partners ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Optimize Partner — area 1748 (hub derived from sl_area_hub)
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/partners/optimize?area_id=1748

###

### Optimize Partner — area 1 (has ShopUp SLA breach data)
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/partners/optimize?area_id=1

# ─── Hubs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Hub Profitability — hub 129 (active hub with real volume)
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/hubs/129/profitability

###

### Hub Model Advice — hub 129
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/hubs/129/model-advice

###

### Hub Profitability — hub 136 (second highest volume)
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/hubs/136/profitability

###

### Get Hub Costs — hub 129, Feb 2026
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/hubs/129/costs?year=2026&month=2

###

### Upsert Hub Costs — hub 129, Feb 2026
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/hubs/129/costs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "year": 2026,
  "month": 2,
  "rent": 80000,
  "employee_cost": 150000,
  "utility_cost": 15000,
  "maintenance_cost": 10000,
  "other_cost": 5000,
  "notes": "Feb 2026 costs — hub 129"
}
